00:01:25.380 --> 00:01:26.180 align:middle line:10%
>>NOORY: Ha!

00:01:26.180 --> 00:01:30.000 align:middle line:10%
>>APOLLO: And I was being
told this story about reality,

00:01:30.000 --> 00:01:33.030 align:middle line:10%
