00:01:53.410 --> 00:01:55.020 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Yes, you know it.

00:01:55.020 --> 00:01:56.850 align:middle line:84%
>>APOLLO: There's no
physics explaining

00:01:56.850 --> 00:01:59.490 align:middle line:84%
how someone looking at
you could tingle your neck

00:01:59.490 --> 00:02:02.130 align:middle line:84%
or burn your ears when
they're talking about you.

00:02:02.130 --> 00:02:04.615 align:middle line:84%
