00:02:14.208 --> 00:02:16.930 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: I would stare at their
head to make them turn around.

00:02:16.930 --> 00:02:17.730 align:middle line:90%
>>APOLLO: Yeah.

00:02:17.730 --> 00:02:19.200 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: And I just did it.

00:02:19.200 --> 00:02:22.560 align:middle line:84%
And all of a sudden, maybe
a minute later, the person

00:02:22.560 --> 00:02:24.990 align:middle line:84%
would just turn and
look and look back.

00:02:24.990 --> 00:02:26.500 align:middle line:90%
And I went, it works.

00:02:26.500 --> 00:02:27.300 align:middle line:90%
>>APOLLO: It does.

00:02:27.300 --> 00:02:30.068 align:middle line:84%
