00:02:45.130 --> 00:02:46.110 align:middle line:84%
>>APOLLO: Yeah,
that's always rough.

00:02:46.110 --> 00:02:46.910 align:middle line:90%
[LAUGHS]

00:02:46.910 --> 00:02:50.130 align:middle line:84%
