questions about these things.

00:03:06.780 --> 00:03:09.510 align:middle line:84%
And tried doing some
different experiments.

00:03:09.510 --> 00:03:12.110 align:middle line:84%
Could you feel it if
you look at your hand,

00:03:12.110 --> 00:03:14.160 align:middle line:90%
or if I look at his hand.

00:03:14.160 --> 00:03:16.860 align:middle line:84%
