this little experiment

00:03:16.860 --> 00:03:19.190 align:middle line:84%
where we put our fingers
together like this.

00:03:19.190 --> 00:03:21.990 align:middle line:84%
And I very slowly
separated my fingertips,

00:03:21.990 --> 00:03:24.480 align:middle line:84%
looking at the
space between them.

00:03:24.480 --> 00:03:30.020 align:middle line:84%
And suddenly, I saw this stringy
fluid between my fingertips.

00:03:30.020 --> 00:03:33.180 align:middle line:84%
And I could feel
it, like a vibration

00:03:33.180 --> 00:03:34.320 align:middle line:90%
going into my fingers.

00:03:34.320 --> 00:03:36.225 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Almost like
a charge of energy.

00:03:36.225 --> 00:03:37.025 align:middle line:90%
>>APOLLO: Yeah.

00:03:37.025 --> 00:03:40.020 align:middle line:84%
And as a 15-year-old kid,
I was like, oh my god.

00:03:40.020 --> 00:03:41.550 align:middle line:90%
I found the force.

00:03:41.550 --> 00:03:42.570 align:middle line:90%
The force is real!

00:03:42.570 --> 00:03:44.850 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: You might have.

00:03:44.850 --> 00:03:46.800 align:middle line:84%
>>APOLLO: But a lot
of people, I think,

00:03:46.800 --> 00:03:48.880 align:middle line:90%
have that kind of experience.

00:03:48.880 --> 00:03:53.460 align:middle line:84%
