much of a scientific inquiry

00:03:53.460 --> 00:03:56.400 align:middle line:84%
to my mind and the way
that I was exploring things

00:03:56.400 --> 00:03:57.870 align:middle line:90%
that I couldn't stop there.

00:03:57.870 --> 00:04:01.080 align:middle line:84%
I hid objects on the other side
of the room and had my friend,

00:04:01.080 --> 00:04:03.690 align:middle line:84%
