them using his hand,

00:04:03.690 --> 00:04:05.520 align:middle line:90%
or me doing it with mine.

00:04:05.520 --> 00:04:07.500 align:middle line:84%
We tried blindfolded
martial arts.

00:04:07.500 --> 00:04:10.380 align:middle line:90%
How fast could we go?

00:04:10.380 --> 00:04:13.100 align:middle line:84%
And the more I
explored this field--

00:04:13.100 --> 00:04:14.850 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: That was
pretty fast, by the way.

00:04:14.850 --> 00:04:15.683 align:middle line:90%
>>APOLLO: Thank you.

00:04:15.683 --> 00:04:17.790 align:middle line:90%
I can go much faster.

00:04:17.790 --> 00:04:20.100 align:middle line:84%
The more I explored
this field, the more

00:04:20.100 --> 00:04:25.020 align:middle line:84%
