so many of the missing

00:04:25.020 --> 00:04:32.640 align:middle line:84%
pieces in my school studies,
in geology, in astrophysics,

00:04:32.640 --> 00:04:37.440 align:middle line:84%
and provided a groundwork for
a much deeper understanding

00:04:37.440 --> 00:04:40.620 align:middle line:84%
of how consciousness is
related to spacetime.

00:04:40.620 --> 00:04:42.360 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Is there a
science behind it?

00:04:42.360 --> 00:04:43.690 align:middle line:90%
Or is it something else?

00:04:43.690 --> 00:04:46.120 align:middle line:84%
>>APOLLO: There is absolutely
a science behind it.

00:04:46.120 --> 00:04:48.477 align:middle line:84%
And I would love to
explore that with you.

00:04:48.477 --> 00:04:50.310 align:middle line:84%
