00:05:01.172 --> 00:05:02.130 align:middle line:90%
>>APOLLO: That's right.

00:05:02.130 --> 00:05:07.410 align:middle line:84%
It's changed a little bit
more recently, because of some

00:05:07.410 --> 00:05:10.087 align:middle line:84%
