00:06:23.543 --> 00:06:24.460 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Oh, there is?

00:06:24.460 --> 00:06:24.630 align:middle line:90%
>>APOLLO: There is.

00:06:24.630 --> 00:06:25.770 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: What is that?

00:06:25.770 --> 00:06:27.910 align:middle line:84%
>>APOLLO: Well,
interestingly enough,

00:06:27.910 --> 00:06:31.170 align:middle line:84%
if you have the same kind
of double slit experiment,

00:06:31.170 --> 00:06:34.260 align:middle line:84%
