assistant at the patent office

00:13:57.310 --> 00:13:59.630 align:middle line:10%
when, in his spare
time, he cranked down

00:13:59.630 --> 00:14:02.900 align:middle line:10%
some of the most remarkable
theories, theories

00:14:02.900 --> 00:14:06.500 align:middle line:10%
that remain the crux of
classical physics today.

00:14:06.500 --> 00:14:09.110 align:middle line:10%
Einstein once said,
any intelligent fool

00:14:09.110 --> 00:14:11.690 align:middle line:10%
can make things bigger
and more complex.

00:14:11.690 --> 00:14:14.120 align:middle line:10%
It takes a touch of genius
