get to really small things

00:30:06.670 --> 00:30:07.930 align:middle line:90%
and back.

00:30:07.930 --> 00:30:09.910 align:middle line:84%
And I thought, well,
that's really interesting.

00:30:09.910 --> 00:30:15.460 align:middle line:84%
Because if the pentagram is
required to curve spacetime,

00:30:15.460 --> 00:30:19.030 align:middle line:84%
