curved gravitational field.

00:30:34.210 --> 00:30:39.800 align:middle line:84%
And that's going to enable
this sort of phi spiral

00:30:39.800 --> 00:30:42.520 align:middle line:84%
perfect weave that's
going to create

00:30:42.520 --> 00:30:45.580 align:middle line:84%
a pattern from everything
small to everything big.

00:30:45.580 --> 00:30:47.300 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Why does this happen?

00:30:47.300 --> 00:30:47.650 align:middle line:90%
>>APOLLO: Why does it happen?

